{"word":"ἄναυδος","slug":"ἄναυδος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄναυδος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:αὐδή'><el>αὐδή</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>speechless, silent</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>preventing speech, silencing</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>like <el>ἀναύδητος</el>, <i>unutterable</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}